EECS Senior Gift License Plate Frame

history.content:
Hello!

I'm a graduating senior in EECS, and I've noticed that several of my friends have received a graduation gift in the mail. It's a license plate frame from the EECS department. 

I haven't received anything yet, and I'm wondering if it's because I'm technically on the Summer 2019 degree list. If so, is there a way I can pick up my gift early? Will I not be able to get it until Summer 2019? Who can I ask about this?

Thanks for your help!
